reviewText: WAY short on content!  I was very disappointed.  I would like to have had more discussion on cord weights/sizes.  Also would have liked to have known how to wrap the butt cap.  There were no supplies and tools shown or listed, but at the end he referenced having shown them.  Not worth the $.

I was expecting more instructional content

the weave for the grip handle is useful the the turkshead information was lacking

the product was shipped on time and was as expected
